[Term]
id: LANG:00000000
name: Language
def: "A language is a structured system of communication. Language, in a broader sense, is the method of communication that involves the use of – particularly human – languages. See https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Language" []
property_value: IAO:0000112 "English is a subClass of Language.  A person has a disposition (capability) with respect to an instance of language for that person.  If two people speak english, they speak instances of english (not identical) that are each instances of the class English." xsd:string
property_value: IAO:0000116 "Very early development.  Change is nearly certain." xsd:string
